{"tid":1557654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美政府歸還華為扣留貨物，口交部：從事實上承認其行為違法性","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:51:34.000Z","uid":28970,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8567543afcc7de5af53ba1324c23c62674a6b5","tid":1557654,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"美政府歸還華為扣留貨物，外交部迴應：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從事實上承認其行為的違法性和隨意性。美方濫用國家力量打壓特定的中國企業，既不光彩也不道德。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n外交部發言人華春瑩表示，「我看到了有關的報道。美國政府近日將兩年前無故扣押的一批電信設備歸還給華為公司，就從事實上承認了其行為的違法性和隨意性。中方堅決反對美方在拿不出任何證據的情況下誣陷中國企業，並且濫用國家的力量打壓特定的中國企業，這種行為既不光彩也不道德，更是對美方一貫標榜的市場經濟原則的否定，將嚴重損害美國自身的形象和信譽，也將嚴重影響各國企業對於和美國開展合作的信心。」"},{"pid":"c9266f98918c63e7404a718647b915609694d79e","tid":1557654,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3377a6e2d47db32eaab4d62a40c35e75dcaa75","tid":1557654,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"120ceec1edb657689b564ef28176b003b7e782ad","tid":1557654,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:06:33.000Z","msg":"兩年前<br />\n<br />\n已變電子垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d708fced01c55d938ad0ac93f634693942a3f3b","tid":1557654,"uid":24853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"120ceec1edb657689b564ef28176b003b7e782ad","tid":1557654,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:06:33.000Z","msg":"兩年前<br />\n<br />\n已變電子垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"本身都係"},{"pid":"9a41136104e1157d405fe9f6243c7b5f1f9adff1","tid":1557654,"uid":28970,"like":